text: Paranonychidae is a family of armoured harvestmen in the order Opiliones. There are about 6 genera and at least 20 described species in Paranonychidae. ==Genera== * Kainonychus Suzuki, 1975 * Kaolinonychus Suzuki, 1975 * Metanonychus Briggs, 1971 * Paranonychus Briggs, 1971 * Sclerobunus Banks, 1893 * Zuma C.J. Goodnight & M.L. Goodnight, 1942 ==References== ==Further reading== * * Category:Harvestmen
